WEBVTT

00:01:57.080 --> 00:02:00.280
And yet a desire to understand 
this fear also came alive.

00:02:00.840 --> 00:02:03.430
How is sexual violence related to fear?

00:02:03.510 --> 00:02:06.510
With this question in mind,
I started "Blank Noise,"

00:02:06.700 --> 00:02:10.569
a group where people
like you and me got together.

00:02:10.639 --> 00:02:13.200
We believe we are "Action Heroes."

00:02:13.360 --> 00:02:17.200
We look at our fears by staring them 
in the face and meeting them head on.

00:02:17.230 --> 00:02:19.160
We awaken the power and capability

00:02:19.160 --> 00:02:23.530
within us to become part of a movement
towards creating a safe environment.

00:02:23.610 --> 00:02:27.140
Our aim is to stop sexual violence.

00:02:27.530 --> 00:02:30.480
Ten years ago, I asked women 
on the streets of Bangalore